<div class="less-width">
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <p>If you'd like, go ahead and leave me a message here. If you would like to get in contact with me more quickly, feel free to send me an email, call me, or send me a message on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/haydenhoopes/">LinkedIn</a>.</p>
    <form action="<%= urlPrefix %>/users/messages" method="POST">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 col-s-12 margin-sm">
                <label for="title">Title</label>
                <input type="text" name="title" id="title">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 col-s-12 margin-sm">
                <label for="message">Message</label>
                <textarea name="message" id="message" ></textarea>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="margin-sm">
            <input type="submit" value="Submit" class="button full-width">
        </div>
    </form>
</div>
